Class NonSyntheticEntryFilter<T>

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.coherence.jcache.common.NonSyntheticEntryFilter<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExternalizableLite, PortableObject, Filter<T>, EntryFilter<Object,T>, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
LocalCacheAsynchronousMapListener.NonSyntheticEntryFilter, PartitionedCacheAsynchronousMapListener.NonSyntheticEntryFilter
public abstract class NonSyntheticEntryFilter<T> extends Object implements EntryFilter<Object,T>, PortableObject, ExternalizableLite
Server side filter to filter out both coherence and jcache synthetic events.

Coherence 12.1.3
